AWS CloudTrail

Provides, compliance & audit for AWS account
- all activities are logged
- can send trail to S3
- if need to look at an API call, use cloudtrail

AWS Atifact (not really a service)

- access to aws compliance documents & aws agreements
- PCI (payment card industry) reports

AWS Audit Manager

- assess risk & complaince of aws workloads
- continuous audit aws services usage & prepare audits
- generates reports of complaince along with evidence folders
